{"id":428574,"date":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":22}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"254","ytitle":"","mtitle":"火把","ftitle":"","authors":["田间"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火把是亚非作家会议标帜之一，我为它作这一首歌。并赠锡兰的一位革命作家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象火把一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把大厅照亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绛色的袈裟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来椰林的花香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰林战士怒斥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义灾殃——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“它也会落在穿袈裟的身上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这使我想到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰林里一古庙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那新生之火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把魔鬼烧掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伪善者的面孔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要把它剥掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“普罗米修士”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将在烈火中大笑!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为你歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这椰林的星光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星与星相接，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是美丽的诗行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人们请记着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代这是疆场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚非两只巨手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早把火把点亮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的椰林之乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由的晨钟已敲响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年二月，从开罗归国途中，记于香港某山顶"}]}